**What it is:** Processing milk into products — pasteurized milk, curd, paneer, cheese, butter, ghee, ice cream, flavored milk.

**Players:** Amul (big), Mother Dairy (big), Hatsun (Indian, big), Heritage Foods (Indian), Parag Milk (Indian).

