### 🟡 333. Textile & Fabric Recycling

**What it is:** Processing textile waste — factory off-cuts, old garments, fabric scraps — into recycled fiber, yarn, or products.

**Players:** Panipat recycling cluster (Indian, biggest in world), individual recyclers, fashion brands with take-back programs.

**Model:** Product Sale 📦 | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

