### 🟡 336. Oil & Lubricant Recycling

**What it is:** Collecting and re-refining used motor oil, industrial lubricants, transformer oil into base oil for reuse.

**Players:** Individual re-refiners, Indian Oil (collects used oil), authorized recyclers.

**Model:** Product Sale 📦 | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 📜 CPCB authorization mandatory · ⚙ Contamination (water, metals, soot) must be removed · 💰 Re-refining plant ₹50L-5Cr · 📈 Informal sector collects and burns used oil (pollution + competition).

**Mistake:** Not getting CPCB authorization. Unauthorized re-refining is illegal. Authorized re-refiners get preferential access to used oil from large generators.

**One-liner:** Re-refine used oil — get CPCB authorization for legal operation and preferential used oil access.

