### 🔴 340. Precious Metal Extraction (Gold, Silver)

**What it is:** Extracting gold, silver, platinum group metals from electronic waste, industrial catalysts, jewelry scrap.

**Players:** Umicore (Belgium, big), individual gold refiners, authorized e-waste recyclers.

**Model:** Product Sale 📦 | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 🧠 Refining chemistry expertise · 📜 Hallmarking for gold products, CPCB for processing · 💰 Assaying and refining equipment · ⚙ Security — dealing with valuable metals.

**Mistake:** Not having proper assaying (purity testing) capability. You must know exactly how much gold is in scrap BEFORE buying it. Without assaying, you'll overpay for scrap and lose on every transaction.

**One-liner:** Extract precious metals — proper assaying capability before buying is essential; without it, you're guessing and losing.

