### 🔴 345. Hazardous Waste Management

**What it is:** Collecting, transporting, treating, and disposing of hazardous industrial waste — chemical sludge, heavy metals, expired chemicals, contaminated materials.

**Players:** Ramky Enviro (Indian, big), Geocycle (big), authorized TSDF operators.

**Model:** Service Fee 🔧 | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 📜 CPCB/SPCB authorization — most regulated waste category · 💰 TSDF (Treatment, Storage, Disposal Facility) ₹5Cr-50Cr · 🧠 Chemical and environmental engineering expertise · ⚙ Transportation in hazmat vehicles · 📜 Manifesting and tracking paperwork.

**Mistake:** Not maintaining meticulous paperwork. Every kilogram of hazardous waste must be documented from generator to disposal. Missing records = regulatory shutdown.

**One-liner:** Manage hazardous waste — the most regulated waste category; meticulous documentation is survival.

