### 🟡 357. Zero-Waste Consulting

**What it is:** Advising organizations on reducing waste — waste audits, waste reduction strategies, circular economy implementation, sustainability reporting.

**Players:** Individual sustainability consultants, Saahas Zero Waste (Indian), global consulting firms' sustainability practices.

**Model:** Service Fee 🔧 | **Revenue:** ⚡ Fast.

**Challenges:** 📈 ESG/sustainability is trending — many new entrants · 🧠 Must have genuine waste management expertise · ⚙ Clients expect measurable reduction metrics · 💰 Small businesses can't afford consulting.

**Mistake:** Being theoretical without actionable results. Companies hire you to REDUCE waste, not write reports about waste. Show measurable kg/month reduction.

**One-liner:** Consult on zero waste — deliver measurable waste reduction numbers, not just reports and frameworks.

